♪Cuddled in the cold wind♪

28
00:01:53,100 --> 00:01:56,780
♪For so long♪

29
00:01:57,380 --> 00:01:58,820
♪When we meet again♪

30
00:01:58,860 --> 00:02:00,620
♪Snowflakes falling on our shoulders♪

31
00:02:01,580 --> 00:02:03,020
♪Never thought at this moment♪

32
