♪But can no longer embrace each other♪

35
00:02:13,180 --> 00:02:15,420
♪And stay forever♪

36
00:02:15,740 --> 00:02:17,220
♪We missed each other♪

37
00:02:17,260 --> 00:02:19,340
♪When the snow was falling♪

38
