42
00:02:29,310 --> 00:02:30,830
(He's not here. Search that area.)

43
00:02:31,990 --> 00:02:32,740
(Fan out!)

44
00:02:33,740 --> 00:02:34,550
Nie Zhen,

45
00:02:34,870 --> 00:02:36,310
are you sure Second Young Master is safe?

46
00:02:38,620 --> 00:02:40,060
He's going to suffer a bit.

47
00:02:40,550 --> 00:02:42,110
But he'll live.

48
00:02:42,900 --> 00:02:44,590
So how did you convince him?

49
00:02:46,180 --> 00:02:47,590
Because I'm Nie Zhen.

50
00:02:47,940 --> 00:02:48,870
I don't lose.

51
00:02:51,710 --> 00:02:53,110
What were you thinking?

52
00:02:53,180 --> 00:02:55,340
You're putting your life
on the line running away.

53
00:02:56,220 --> 00:02:57,710
Because I wanted to see you.

54
00:03:02,340 --> 00:03:03,500
When the time is right,

55
00:03:03,780 --> 00:03:05,310
we'll go back
and rescue Second Young Master.

56
00:03:09,430 --> 00:03:10,270
Xiaodie,

57
