I know you're worried about Miss Shen.

58
00:03:15,030 --> 00:03:16,900
But she's been through so much.

59
00:03:17,180 --> 00:03:18,500
She's holding a grudge.

60
00:03:19,550 --> 00:03:20,830
And that grudge has made her

61
00:03:21,270 --> 00:03:22,500
an unwitting tool of someone else.

62
00:03:22,740 --> 00:03:24,030
Is that Mr. Zhao?

63
00:03:24,390 --> 00:03:26,500
The guy
who drugged you disguised as a doctor

64
00:03:26,740 --> 00:03:28,460
