65
00:03:29,180 --> 00:03:29,900
That's right.

66
00:03:32,270 --> 00:03:33,740
I've been trying to gather intel on him.

67
00:03:34,460 --> 00:03:36,270
But my efforts have not been fruitful.

68
00:03:41,500 --> 00:03:42,180
Nie Zhen,

69
00:03:42,180 --> 00:03:42,460
actually...

70
00:03:42,460 --> 00:03:44,150
You're trying to bail Miss Shen out,

71
00:03:44,310 --> 00:03:45,180
aren't you?

72
00:03:47,180 --> 00:03:48,780
She's the most important person
in my life.

73
00:03:50,310 --> 00:03:52,180
If it's just pure hatred for me,

74
00:03:52,460 --> 00:03:53,460
I can live with that.

75
00:03:53,900 --> 00:03:56,460
But if she's being used by someone
with hidden motives,

76
00:03:57,270 --> 00:03:59,180
I will do everything I can
to get her out of this big mess.

77
00:04:03,150 --> 00:04:03,900
Xiaodie,

78
00:04:05,740 --> 00:04:06,990
just leave everything to me.

79
00:04:07,150 --> 00:04:08,900
When we get out of Hongzhou,

80
00:04:09,460 --> 00:04:11,060
I'll get to the bottom of this.

81
00:04:17,710 --> 00:04:18,630
Xiaodie,

82
00:04:19,030 --> 00:04:20,420
do you not trust me?

83
00:04:21,830 --> 00:04:23,030
I knew

84
00:04:23,510 --> 00:04:26,710
Second Young Master
would tell you about my whole plan.

85
00:04:27,460 --> 00:04:28,510
I just knew it.

86
00:04:30,190 --> 00:04:31,710
Are you keeping something back from him?

87
00:04:34,390 --> 00:04:36,270
All these diversions

88
00:04:36,830 --> 00:04:39,030
didn't exactly
divert Mr. Zhao's attention.

89
00:04:39,830 --> 00:04:41,460
There has to be a hostage.

90
00:04:43,070 --> 00:04:44,070
Xiaodie,

91
00:04:44,070 --> 00:04:44,950
