92
00:04:44,950 --> 00:04:46,190
You're the one doing stupid things.

93
00:04:48,070 --> 00:04:49,590
You got out of there too soon.

94
00:04:50,510 --> 00:04:52,710
Only when we're alive can there be hope.
Do you understand?

95
00:04:52,710 --> 00:04:53,710
We'll talk about it

96
00:04:54,070 --> 00:04:56,150
