105
00:05:16,030 --> 00:05:16,830
Xiaodie...

106
00:05:17,180 --> 00:05:21,460
♪There it is, the predictable truth♪

107
00:05:25,980 --> 00:05:26,780
Nie Zhen.

108
00:05:28,830 --> 00:05:30,070
You said

109
00:05:30,980 --> 00:05:33,630
we would eventually

110
00:05:34,300 --> 00:05:35,540
