111
00:05:36,980 --> 00:05:38,070
I haven't forgotten that.

112
00:05:42,510 --> 00:05:43,540
Stay safe.

113
00:05:45,830 --> 00:05:47,030
I'll be right here when you get back.

114
00:05:47,780 --> 00:05:51,820
♪My sad dinner♪

115
00:05:51,900 --> 00:05:56,860
♪Pain disguised as sweets♪

116
00:05:56,860 --> 00:05:57,750
I have something to report!

117
00:06:05,980 --> 00:06:09,710
Do you have any message that you want me
to take to the Ivory Bridge?

118
00:06:14,630 --> 00:06:15,950
Unlike you,

119
00:06:16,190 --> 00:06:18,540
Xiaodie has always been a wise woman.

120
00:06:22,540 --> 00:06:24,190
Just think this through.

121
